This is a fork of the original http://suitmymind.github.com/ubuntu-machine however it has been modified to have slightly more focus on setting a machine up for PHP development.

This is used to setup no only local development virtual machines but also production slices at Slicehost.

= View the original docs here :
http://suitmymind.github.com/ubuntu-machine


= Usage

1. git clone git://github.com/alistairstead/ubuntu-machine.git ./my_new_server
2. cd my_new_server
3. cap machine:initial_setup
4. cap machine:configure
5. cap machine:install_dev_tools